wBkM"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-73" id="cite_note-73"><a href="./Opera#cite_ref-73" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-73" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://opera.emergingpictures.com" id="mwBkQ">Emerging Pictures</a> <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20080630062054/http://opera.emergingpictures.com/" about="#mwt299" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"webarchive","href":"./Template:Webarchive"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"https://web.archive.org/web/20080630062054/http://opera.emergingpictures.com/"},"date":{"wt":"30 June 2008"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBkU">Archived</a><span about="#mwt299" id="mwBkY"> 30 June 2008 at the </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine" about="#mwt299" id="mwBkc">Wayback Machine</a><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Webarchive_template_wayback_links" about="#mwt299" id="mwBkg"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-74" id="cite_note-74"><a href="./Opera#cite_ref-74" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-74" class="mw-reference-text">"Where to See Opera at the Movies" sidebar p. W10 in June 21–22, 2008 <i id="mwBkk">The Wall Street Journal</i>.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-75" id="cite_note-75"><a href="./Opera#cite_ref-75" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-75" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Classic_FM_(UK)" title="Classic FM (UK)" id="mwBko">Classic FM</a> (26 August 2009). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.classicfm.com/composers/wagner/news/glyndebourne-announces-downloadable-opera/#k4oDKFadPL9Jyl05.97" id="mwBks">"Download Glyndebourne"</a>. Retrieved 21 May 2016.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-76" id="cite_not